headline: Eastman Earns Equality 100 Award in Human Rights Campaign Foundation’s 2025 Corporate Equality Index
summary: KINGSPORT, Tenn., January 07, 2025--Eastman Chemical Company (NYSE:EMN) has received a score of 100 on the Human Rights Campaign Foundation’s (HRCF) 2025 Corporate Equality Index.
